[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0963","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1126","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.1 及更早版本创建文件时使用了不安全的权限设置，导致本地攻击者可读取 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 以及名称以 \"DPR_\" 开头的临时文件，从中获取包含用户名、密码和 SNMP 团体字串在内的敏感配置信息。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，但需要系统本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1126"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.547","remediation":"将 Cisco Resource Manager 升级至 CiscoWorks Resource Manager Essentials (RME) 后续受支持版本；同时立即对 swim_swd.log、swim_debug.log、dbi_debug.log 及 DPR_* 临时文件设置仅 root 可读权限（chmod 600），并清除日志中明文存储的用户名、密码及 SNMP 团体字串；限制仅授权管理员具有本地系统访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-086.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1575","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87017/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1126.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ea4986e5-e053-4e4f-b784-9c4adf62a083.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0963.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0959","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1124","title":"Adobe ColdFusion HTTP客户端安全绕过漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion 中的 mainframeset.cfm 页面存在安全绕过漏洞。该页面提供的 HTTP 客户端功能允许远程攻击者提交目标 URL，服务器会代表攻击者向内网其他端口上的 Web 页面发起请求，由于请求来源被伪造为本地回环地址（localhost），因此可以绕过基于 IP 地址或端口的访问控制策略。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞扫描内网端口、访问内部受限资源，导致敏感信息泄露或进一步的横向攻击。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1124"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.283","remediation":"升级至 ColdFusion 5.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 mainframeset.cfm SSRF 绕过问题）；若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面通过 URL 重写规则或访问控制列表（ACL）禁止外部请求访问 /mainframeset.cfm 路径；同时在防火墙上限制应用服务器对外部端口的出站连接，防止被利用为内网探测代理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstorm.securify.com/mag/phrack/phrack54/P54-08","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1124","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1124.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v/GHSA-c8gw-jg28-8m4v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0957","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1117","title":"IBM AIX lquerypv 本地文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 及 4.2 系统中的 lquerypv 工具在解析 -h 命令行参数时未对文件路径进行充分校验，导致存在任意文件读取漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 -h 参数传入目标文件路径（如 /etc/passwd 或系统配置文件），越权读取本无权访问的敏感文件内容，造成信息泄露。该漏洞利用条件要求攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，虽然无需 root 权限但无法远程触发，故整体危害较低，CVSS 评分 2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1117"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.383","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3 或更高版本，IBM 已通过 APAR 修复此问题。如无法升级，以 root 执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/lquerypv` 移除 setuid 权限，阻止普通用户以特权运行该命令。同时通过文件系统 ACL 限制可执行 `lquerypv` 的用户范围作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420195&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&w=2&r=1&s=lquerypv&q=b","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/455","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19345","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1117","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1117.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000997.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0947","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1105","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 远程任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用 NetWare 网络的远程管理和文件共享功能时存在设计缺陷，当管理员远程登录系统后会自动创建隐藏的 C$ 共享目录，且未对共享访问权限进行有效限制。远程攻击者无需高级权限，只需通过网络映射该驱动器即可读取目标系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 操作系统，利用方式简单，危害主要为信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1105"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.947","remediation":"立即禁用 Remote Administration 和 File Sharing for NetWare Networks 功能（进入控制面板 → 网络 → 服务，移除 File and Printer Sharing for NetWare Networks 及相关绑定）。由于 Windows 95 已终止支持，建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 版本，并确保 SMB 服务不暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7231.php","http://www.net-security.sk/bugs/NT/netware1.html","http://www.zdnet.com/eweek/reviews/1016/tr42bug.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/8fb60f1e10e801132244052aaca5ef57fba4fd01/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1105","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88095/info.html","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0944","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1104","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 密码列表文件弱加密权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用密码缓存时对密码列表（.pwl）文件使用弱加密算法进行存储，本地攻击者可通过直接访问该文件并利用加密缺陷破译其中的明文密码，从而获取系统登录凭据并提升自身权限。该漏洞影响所有启用密码缓存的 Windows 95 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。微软已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1104"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.830","remediation":"Windows 95 已停止支持且无官方安全更新。建议立即禁用密码缓存：打开控制面板 → 密码 → 更改密码 → 点击\"开始使用\"并取消勾选所有密码缓存选项，同时删除 %WINDIR% 目录下所有 .pwl 文件。作为根本解决方案，应升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）以消除此风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418931&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88536273725787&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88540877601866&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q140/5/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/71.php","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1104","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000995.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0942","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1102","title":"BSD lpr 本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 lpr 打印服务组件存在任意文件写入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击方式，在多次调用 lpr 命令（约 1000 次）后触发竞争条件，导致以 lp 权限创建或覆盖系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1、BSD 4.3、A/UX 2.0.1 及其他基于 BSD 的操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1102"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.580","remediation":"建议升级至现代 BSD 发行版（FreeBSD 4.0+/OpenBSD 2.0+）或改用 CUPS 替代 lpr 打印系统。如因兼容性无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr`，但会限制普通用户使用打印功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-25.shtml","http://www.aenigma.net/resources/maillist/bugtraq/1994/0091.htm","http://www.phreak.org/archives/security/8lgm/8lgm.lpr","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1102","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1102.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89