g` 的 `Debugger` 值清空或删除该注册表项。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以获得完整的注册表访问控制支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90222453431604&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q103/8/61.asp","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-029.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1044","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19798","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1084","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1084.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3v3p-5qg2-fr76/GHSA-3v3p-5qg2-fr76.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1044/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1084.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0931.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0921","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1074","title":"Webmin 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"Webmin 0.5 之前版本存在认证机制缺陷，对有效用户名的登录密码尝试次数未作限制，远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统实施暴力枚举攻击，通过不断尝试常用或弱口令来猜测系统管理员密码，从而获取 Webmin 管理面板的访问权限并最终控制服务器。该漏洞影响 Webmin 0.5 及更早版本，属于高风险缺陷，攻击门槛较低，且无需提前获取任何认证凭据。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1074"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.017","remediation":"立即升级 Webmin 至 0.5 或更高版本，该版本已限制同一用户名的密码尝试次数。如无法升级，可在 Webmin 前端配置额外认证模块（如 fail2ban）限制登录频率，并在防火墙层面将 Webmin 管理端口（默认 10000）仅对可信 IP 开放，同时启用强密码策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9138","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/98","http://www.webmin.com/webmin/changes.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1074","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1074.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/robinzixuan/attackmap/blob/3e50ba1e011308b7d6ea18a627132f0a357f36c0/Asia/bruteresult.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000988.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--39926f99-82f5-4fec-ad30-6de2b1dd04dc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0921.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0893","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1043","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0/5.5 NNTP 和 SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.0 和 5.5 版本在处理畸形的 NNTP（网络新闻传输协议）数据或 SMTP（简单邮件传输协议）数据时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标邮件服务器发送特制的畸形数据包触发服务进程错误，导致 Exchange 服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0 和 5.5，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1043"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.187","remediation":"将 Microsoft Exchange Server 升级至 5.5 Service Pack 3（SP3）或更高版本（Exchange 5.0 用户需先迁移至 5.5 再安装 SP3）。如无法升级，可在服务器管理中禁用 NNTP 虚拟服务器服务，并在防火墙策略中限制 TCP 25（SMTP）和 TCP 119（NNTP）端口的访问来源为可信 IP 段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-007","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1043","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1043.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88091/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0890","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1042","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.0 和 1.1 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。由于程序创建的日志文件及临时文件权限设置为全局可读，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷读取这些文件，从而获取用户ID、密码及SNMP团体字符串等敏感凭据信息。此漏洞影响CRM 1.0和1.1版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS评分1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1042"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.067","remediation":"升级 Cisco Resource Manager 至 1.2 或更高版本以修复默认文件权限问题；对手动创建的日志目录和临时文件目录执行 chmod 600 或 640，仅允许 CRM 服务账户读写；通过文件系统 ACL 限制本地非授权用户访问 /var/log/crm 及临时目录；定期审计日志文件权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87012/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0889","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1035","title":"Microsoft IIS HTTP GET 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 及 4.0 版本（x86 和 Alpha 平台）在处理畸形的 HTTP GET 请求时存在缺陷，远程未经认证的攻击者可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 GET 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响运行 IIS 3.0/4.0 的 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。官方建议升级至更高版 IIS 版本或部署安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1035"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.207","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS98-019 提供的对应平台热修补丁（IIS 3.0/4.0 for x86/Alpha），或升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 更高版本。由于 IIS 3.0 和 4.0 均已停止技术支持多年，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的操作系统及 IIS 版本（如 Windows Server 2022 + IIS 10），从根本上消除此漏洞风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q192/2/96.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-019","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1823","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1035","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1035.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1035.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0579","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0815","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP Agent 内存泄漏拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP 服务代理存在内存泄漏漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统 SNMP 服务发送大量查询请求，导致系统内存资源被持续消耗直至耗尽，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP5 之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。安装 SP5 及以上版本补丁可修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0815"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.917","remediation":"升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，SP5 已修复 SNMP Agent 的内存泄漏问题。对于无法升级的系统，可在防火墙规则中限制对 UDP 端口 161 的访问，仅允许受信任的管理站发起 SNMP 查询，以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q196/2/70.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1974","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A952"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0572","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0808","title":"ISC DHCP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC DHCP 服务器（dhcpd）1.0 和 2.0 版本存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 DHCP 服务器发送包含超长选项字段的恶意数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务，甚至可能利用该漏洞执行任意代码。该漏洞影响大量使用 ISC DHCP 服务的网络环境，攻击条件简单，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0808"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.993","remediation":"建议立即升级 ISC DHCP 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 dhcpd 1.0/2.0 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 DHCP 服务器 UDP 67/68 端口的访问，仅允许受信任的子网段通信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-053.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925960&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml"}]